These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, baking, rock-climbing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, balloon-flower
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, brazilian, spanish
City: new-york, rome, paris
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, green, amber
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, van
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
 3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the spanish##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is the brazilian##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person traveling to rome and the person driving the van##2
10. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
11. the person who growsdaffodil is the person traveling to paris##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Hobby          | gardening   | rock-climbing            | baking     |
| Flower           | daffodil | balloon-flower | daisy |
| Nationality   | mexican      | spanish               | brazilian        |
| City           | paris        | new-york         | rome   |
| Color         | amber     | green      | orange       |
| Transport     | van        | train              | boat       |

