.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, april, june
3 different games are played: chess, whist, scrabble
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking, board-games
House: cape-cod, craftsman, palace
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, daisy
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person playing chess##2
 6. the cape-cod house is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who growsbegonia##2
 7. the person drinking milk is the craftsman house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | lemonade | milk        |
| Birthday          | april   | june    | october        |
| Game   | chess    | whist | scrabble |
| Hobby   | board-games   | filmmaking  | woodworking         |
| House           | palace    | cape-cod | craftsman       |
| Flower     | marigold   | daisy    | begonia  |

