.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, september, october
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, lilac, purple
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, ritmeester, cain
There are 3 different nationalities: french, malaysian, brazilian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, electronic, funk
3 different pets are kept: cat, pony, rat
 1. the french is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 2. the brazilian is the person who likes purple##1
 3. the fan of electronic is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who likes turquise is between the ritmeester-smoker and the owner of the pony##2
 6. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
 8. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 9. the brazilian is on the far right##1
10. the cain-smoker is in an odd position##4
11. the ritmeester-smoker is the malaysian##1
12. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
13. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Birthday      | september        | april     | october          |
| Color          | lilac     | turquise | purple    |
| Cigar         | ritmeester    | oliveros  | cain |
| Nationality           | malaysian | french    | brazilian    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | funk | techno      |
| Pet           | cat          | rat     | pony         |

