.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, subway, motorbike
3 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, ferret
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, snooker
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, soul
House: craftsman, victorian, art-deco
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, siglo, cain
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of d&b is between the siglo-smoker and the owner of the ferret##2
 6. the victorian house is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 8. the person playing canasta is the aristoff-smoker##1
 9. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
10. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
11. the victorian house is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Transport      | subway  | motorbike      | boat        |
| Pet         | ferret   | rat     | lizard |
| Game   | canasta | snooker | monopoly     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | d&b         | soul         |
| House   | craftsman   | art-deco     | victorian      |
| Cigar         | aristoff  | cain     | siglo         |

