 1. the person traveling to paris is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the motorbike##2
 2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 3. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is the person traveling to prague##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
12. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |
