 8. the person who likes paramedic is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person who likes amber is the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the paramedic##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | coffee   | soy-milk   |
| Job          | paramedic    | project-manager    | lawyer |
| Color   | paramedic       | amber   | aquamarine    |
| Transport   | skateboard    | snowmobile | scooter  |
| Flower           | orchid      | amaryllis    | tulip       |
| Cigar         | chaman | pall-mall  | bluemaster   |

