4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
7. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who likes lavender and the person watching satire movies##2
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3

